data.description: Away from the crowd!  Check out this cozy home with amazing views yet in proximity to both State College and Bellefonte.  Boasting an open floor plan connecting the kitchen, dining and family room areas with plenty of natural light, this home also has a finished lower-level rec room, office, or even a potential 3rd bedroom and a half bath, along with a spacious unfinished room that could become more potential living area down the road.  Relax in the evening on your spacious deck off the back or up by the fire circle nestled in the woods.  With newer appliances, water systems, radon mitigation, and more nice functional improvements, this is a great place to start calling a home your own. $5,000 seller assist with an acceptable offer.
